{"tid":1802921,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"我比條仆街挽感情","createTime":"2019-12-29T21:16:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-29T21:34:12.000Z","uid":344406,"like":2,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"ccdf43e9efaaf0c11ebc0dc794044eaaead9a27e","tid":1802921,"uid":344406,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T21:16:36.000Z","msg":"系12月頭我發現左我條仔搵返個ex，之後佢地仲扑左三次野。然後條女仲要走黎打柒我。打到我成隻腳瘀晒，又扯我頭髮。話系我破壞佢地。但系我識條仔個陣佢地已經分左手。<br />\n     條仔話搵反ex系對佢仲有留戀，個ex黎求佢就心軟。佢話好對唔住我，傷害左我，話唔系有心挽我感情。<br />\n     根住我仲發現條仔<span style=\"font-size: large;\">搞大過個條女嘅肚</span>，我好無奈咁成為左受害者之餘仲比人打到傷曬，我應該點做好？"},{"pid":"3d0ff0a447d75c87483bdabb7328b9234d8ef555","tid":1802921,"uid":129856,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T21:19:52.000Z","msg":"分手 放圖<br />\n俾其他人認清呢個人嘅真面目<br />\n佢嘅解釋只係掩飾佢做過嘅仆街野<br />\n唔好再信佢"},{"pid":"ce484b00f5c7ae8bf2e9f2cb1f35621722578864","tid":1802921,"uid":146193,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T21:21:07.000Z","msg":"挽你老母"},{"pid":"d76adb4a8bb69fa69a8e7b70f63005f76e77bc0f","tid":1802921,"uid":293368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T21:21:24.000Z","msg":"Cls 緊係分手"},{"pid":"5419c869dbbf6de8af1587db5f4d2006c9bce6af","tid":1802921,"uid":254923,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T21:22:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JDuh0W5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJDuh0W5.jpg&h=5e171088&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b07c23570fee292ebf6631582651ee7b135e734a","tid":1802921,"uid":78856,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T21:23:03.000Z","msg":"0/10"},{"pid":"ad7e144a9da48364ac26f5eab98d38b83a9ef5be","tid":1802921,"uid":214803,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T21:23:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gCBcPQO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgCBcPQO.jpg&h=8507b63e&s={SIZE}\" />"